	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "8a7b748f-4001-48b6-baca-dd86c0343142",
		"name": "Vantage Finance API – Core Backend",
		"description": "StartFragment\n\nThis collection provides a suite of RESTful endpoints for a role-based financial management system. It implements a robust **Role-Based Access Control (RBAC)** architecture using JWT authentication to distinguish between Admin, Analyst, and Viewer capabilities.\n\n**Key Features:**\n\n- **Secure Authentication:** JWT-based login with password hashing.\n    \n- **User Management:** Admin-only routes for scaling the organization.\n    \n- **Financial Ledger:** CRUD operations for income and expenses with strict validation via Zod.\n    \n- **Dashboard Analytics:** Aggregated insights including net balance and category breakdowns.\n    \n\n**Technical Stack:** Node.js, TypeScript, Express, Prisma ORM, PostgreSQL.\n\nEndFragment",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
		"_exporter_id": "37350753"
	},
